title Sistem Manajemen Perpustakaan Sederhana\n<i>Class Diagram - OOP Implementation</i>

' ========== ABSTRACT CLASS ==========
abstract class LibraryItem {
    {field} # _id: int
    {field} # _title: str
    --
    {method} + {property} title: str
    {method} + {property} item_id: int
    {method} + {abstract} display_info(): void
    {method} + {abstract} get_item_type(): str
}

' ========== CONCRETE CLASSES - BOOK ==========
class Book {
    {field} # _author: str
    {field} # _pages: int
    --
    {method} + {property} author: str
    {method} + {property} pages: str
    {method} + display_info(): void
    {method} + get_item_type(): str
    {method} + __str__(): str
}

' ========== CONCRETE CLASSES - MAGAZINE ==========
class Magazine {
    {field} # _issue: str
    {field} # _month: str
    --
    {method} + {property} issue: str
    {method} + {property} month: str
    {method} + display_info(): void
    {method} + get_item_type(): str
    {method} + __str__(): str
}

' ========== LIBRARY MANAGER CLASS ==========
class Library {
    {field} - __items: list[LibraryItem]
    --
    {method} + add_item(item: LibraryItem): void
    {method} + list_items(): void
    {method} + search_by_title(keyword: str): list
    {method} + search_by_id(item_id: int): LibraryItem | None
    {method} + get_total_items(): int
}

' ========== RELATIONSHIPS ==========
Book --|> LibraryItem : <<extends>>
Magazine --|> LibraryItem : <<extends>>
Library "1" o-- "*" LibraryItem : manages

' ========== NOTES ==========
note right of LibraryItem
    **<<Abstract Base Class>>**
    Mendefinisikan interface umum
    untuk semua item perpustakaan
    
    Menggunakan: abc.ABC
    Access: protected attributes (_)
end note

note right of Book
    **Concrete Subclass**
    Implementasi untuk item BUKU
    
    Override:
    - display_info()
    - get_item_type()
    
    Feature: Property decorator
    untuk encapsulation
end note

note right of Magazine
    **Concrete Subclass**
    Implementasi untuk item MAJALAH
    
    Override:
    - display_info()
    - get_item_type()
    
    Feature: Property decorator
    untuk encapsulation
end note

note right of Library
    **Manager Class**
    Mengelola koleksi perpustakaan
    
    Encapsulation:
    - Private __items list
    - Polymorphism via display_info()
    
    Aggregation: 1 Library : Many Items
end note

